EXTRACTED VALUE: A faithful dog named Old Yeller helps a boy named Travis and his family survive life on the Texas frontier.
Fourteen-year-old Mary Call tries to keep her family together after the death of her sharecropper father.
Short scriptural meditations that the reader can look to for guidance each day or via an index at the back of the book.
What does a young girl do when she wants her ears pierced but her parents say no?
